---
// What We Do Section - Plain text layout, no cards
---

<section id="what-we-do" class="what-we-do">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="headline">Start with the right question.</h2>
    <p class="intro-text">
      We don't just build what you ask for. We discover what your business actually needs.
    </p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">01</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Foundation Discovery</h3>
          <p>We dig into your business patterns to refine your problem statement. Together, we define your product's goals and expectations—the foundation everything else is built on.</p>
          <span class="deliverable"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Clear problem definition, validated business goals, documented expectations</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">02</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Proof of Concept & Research</h3>
          <p>We plan and conduct research with your real end-users. Through structured interviews and testing, we validate assumptions and uncover requirements you didn't know you had.</p>
          <span class="deliverable"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> User insights from actual interviews, validated requirements, research documentation</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">03</span>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Deliverables</h3>
          <p>You receive your first prototype sketch and a comprehensive Business Requirements Specification (BRS)—complete with KPIs. This becomes your roadmap for development.</p>
          <span class="deliverable"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Initial prototype, firm BRS with documented KPIs, development-ready specifications</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="ai-note">
      <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
      We use Generative AI to draft documents and prototypes—but never for thinking. Every insight comes from human analysis of your unique business.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what-we-do {
    background-color: var(--color-navy);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-5xl) var(--space-xl);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width-text);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .headline {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .step-number {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .deliverable {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-cyan);
  }

  .deliverable i {
    margin-top: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-note {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-note i {
    color: var(--color-cyan);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .step {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .step-number {
      width: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .what-we-do {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
    }

    .headline {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
